oint \mathbf {B} \cdot \mathrm {d} {\boldsymbol {\ell }}=3D\mu _{0}I_{\math=
rm {enc} },}"></span>
where the <a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Line_integral" title=3D"=
Line integral">line integral</a> is over any arbitrary loop and <span class=
